[SN]TITLE[SN]
Burnham-on-Sea speed camera flashing constantly

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A broken speed camera in Somerset has begun constantly flashing its main light.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
14 September 2016 Last updated at 08:58 BST
The malfunctioning device was caught on camera with motorists slowly driving past as the light went off every few seconds.
It is located on the A38 at Rooksbridge near Burnham-on-Sea and one theory is that it was struck by lightning.
